#Scripts developed to compute enrichment profiles based on a pangenome matrix
#Hypergeometric test

oh.hypergeometric.R - R script that takes as input a pangenome matrix and returns two tables. One of enrichment betweens PA and NPA and the other between RA and Soil genomes. The tables include two versions of the Hypergeometric test, one in which the values in the matrix are binarized and one in which they are not.

oh.slave_hypergeometric.sh - Shell wrapper to call the hypergeometric.R script

#PhyloGLM
#Because we 
oh.split_matrix_for_pagelphyloglm.R - R script that takes the provided metadata file and the phylogenetic tree and rearranged a provided pangenome matrix to be analized by PhyloGLM. The script automatically process PA/NPA and RA/Soil comparisons. 

oh.split_matrix_for_pagelphyloglm_binarize.R - R script that is equivalent to  oh.split_matrix_for_pagelphyloglm_binarize.R but instead of using raw values, it binarizes the provided pangenome matrix.

oh.slave_split_matrix_for_pagelphyloglm.sh and  oh.slave_split_matrix_for_pagelphyloglm_binarize.sh - Bash scripts that call the oh.split_matrix_for_pagelphyloglm.R oh.split_matrix_for_pagelphyloglm_binarize.R R scripts.

oh.phyloglm.R - R script that runs PhyloGLM over a prepared matrix output either by oh.split_matrix_for_pagelphyloglm.R or oh.split_matrix_for_pagelphyloglm_binarize.R

oh.slave_phyloglm.sh - Bash script that automatizes the call of oh.phyloglm.R.

oh.merge_phyloglm.R - Rscript to concatenate multiple 
#Scoary
oh.create_scoary_input.R - R Script that creates three files per comparison (PA/NPA and RA/Soil). The files created are traits_scoary_pa_npa.tsv matrix_scoary_pa_npa.tsv, tree_scoary_pa_npa.newick, traits_scoary_ra_soil.tsv, matrix_scoary_ra_soil.tsv and tree_scoary_ra_soil.newick. These files are the input to scoary.

oh.slave_create_scoary_input.sh - Sell wrapper to call oh.create_scoary_input.R script.

oh.scoary.sh - Shell script that runs scoary taking the three files created per comparison. E.g oh.scoary.sh traits_scoary_pa_npa.tsv matrix_scoary_pa_npa.tsv tree_scoary_pa_npa.newick

#Bugwas
oh.bugwas.R - RScript that takes a pangenome matrix and run bugwas. The analysis is automatically run for PA/NPa and RA/Soil comparison.

oh.slave_bugwas.sh - Shell wrapper to call oh.bugwas.R.

